title: Prevent Repeated Scheduled/Deadline Tasks From Accumulating
tags: @zettel _method orgmode
roam-id: 4b7f235e-1f54-4d17-a7f3-b70c4e8d22cf
type: text/markdown

- use `++1w` instead of `+1w`.

- add the following into your config

  ``` elisp
  (setq org-agenda-skip-scheduled-if-done t) ;; clear stacked multiple scheduled repeated items when marked as done
  (setq org-agenda-skip-deadline-if-done t) ;; clear stacked multiple deadline repeated items when marked as done
  ```
